{"tid":1896183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【必睇】工會戰線最新攻略：邊抗疫邊打仗","createTime":"2020-02-25T03:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:23:44.000Z","uid":221035,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ea96617c1bf431baec2cd5f6f66c73d4b24caa","tid":1896183,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"工會戰線終極目標：大罷工<br />\n<br />\n手段：<br />\n一、每個行業開工會<br />\n二、工會透過不同方法壯大勢力<br />\n三、招收手足做會員<br />\n四、透過一啲政治事件觸發民衆情緒，在臨界點嘅時候爆發罷工<br />\n<br />\n困難：<br />\n一、唔知工會信唔信得過，無往積<br />\n二、行業太分散，好多不同公司，難集結勢力<br />\n三、手足難相認<br />\n<br />\n解決辦法：<br />\n一、把握宜家疫情嚴重，好多勞資糾紛eg炒人、逼放No Pay Leave，搵工會求助，組織同公司嘅同事一齊爭取<br />\n二、工會幫會員pair up組織企業力量，逐間公司打<br />\n<br />\n效果：工會透過抗疫戰組織企業力量，打case增強實力，同時增加會員信心，亦藉此招收更多會員<br />\n<br />\n額外好處：企業組織同時可以夾手開工會，攞選委票，配合沈旭暉講嘅campaign，滿足埋其他需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有用資源：<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=e6d8b0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHkpetitions.com&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=2b1c0b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hkpetitions.com</a> 團隊最新推出<br />\n7起：起工會神器，不但加速組隊進度，還提供 會章Generator 及已成立工會會章範本 幫助大家提升處理文件效率，最後大家向職登局交上表格和工作證明文件，就完成申請。<br />\n重奪公民權利 保障工人權益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=f556509d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a>"},{"pid":"f8c6f251f3c72272b01b7bbc365510e552cd204a","tid":1896183,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"邊抗疫邊打仗！"},{"pid":"e2150a415cd7aad283fe64a72853a681971a80fc","tid":1896183,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"肺炎過咗就無得咁玩！<br />\n宜家要把握時期！"},{"pid":"c92674ef366a20821fff3e050c2075ee00886833","tid":1896183,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a5431991f81c771251e8b2a7fb6efbcbe24d0b","tid":1896183,"uid":140000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0605cc3a2eb952d78940c3a370cea8936c2b8cf7","tid":1896183,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc3f037bf83364fcff5cd7cde4c8aab44804613","tid":1896183,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"組織工會 <del>進攻功能組別</del> 籌備大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873b450a39214682940658c7387859eba9500236","tid":1896183,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"快速成立工會個重點係做返<br />\n一係組返相同僱主下既工會，先真正有罷工談判能力<br />\n二係搶勞工界別選委票同立法會選票，不過依家太趕只趕到 2022特首果 60 票"},{"pid":"5e954a3f5c5dfa9a96863993a77e3b9428eed062","tid":1896183,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fc3f037bf83364fcff5cd7cde4c8aab44804613","tid":1896183,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"組織工會 <del>進攻功能組別</del> 籌備大三罷<img